OL,3,CTeenager locked up after officer left
OL,4,C'fearing for his life' during riots
OL,6,FA teenager has been given a custodial
OL,7,Fsentence after rocking a police van
OL,8,Fwith an officer inside during riots.
OL,10,FKenzie Roughley, 18, admitted
OL,11,Fattacking a police van during violent
OL,12,Fdisorder in Rotherham earlier this
OL,13,Fmonth.
OL,15,FFootage of the van being rocked from
OL,16,Fside to side, with its rooftop mast
OL,17,Fswinging, was widely shared on social
OL,18,Fmedia during the trouble at a Holiday
OL,19,FInn Express hotel housing more than
OL,20,F200 asylum seekers.
