OL,6,FIn a video played at Sheffield Crown
OL,7,FCourt, the defendant could be seen
OL,8,Fkicking and trying to break into the
OL,9,Fvehicle, which was parked just outside
OL,10,Fa nearby Aldi.
OL,12,FThe court heard how the PCSO inside
OL,13,Fthe van "feared" for his life as he
OL,14,F"felt like the van was about to turn
OL,15,Fover".
