OL,3,CTeenager locked up after officer left
OL,4,C'fearing for his life' during riots
OL,6,FAn impact statement read: "I suddenly
OL,7,Ffelt the vehicle start to rock from
OL,8,Fside to side. I could hear banging and
OL,9,Fkicking. I feared the van may turn
OL,10,Fover, and at the same time I received
OL,11,Fa message from control (asking) me to
OL,12,Fmove out and escape the crowd.
OL,14,F"I got into the cab. I felt the van
OL,15,Fwas going turn over and I feared for
OL,16,Fmy life due to the volatility of the
OL,17,Fcrowd. I started the vehicle and drove
OL,18,Faway."
