OL,6,FMoments before this incident, Roughley
OL,7,Fwas filmed verbally abusing police
OL,8,Fofficers as part of a wider group of
OL,9,Frioters.
OL,11,FBody-worn footage played to the court
OL,12,Fshowed the defendant dropping to the
OL,13,Ffloor and twice attempting to pick up
OL,14,Fwhat appeared to be debris on the
OL,15,Fpavement.
OL,17,FProsecutor Neil Coxon said: "The
OL,18,Fdefendant goes to the ground and
OL,19,Fendeavours to pick something up. It
OL,20,Fappears to be debris from the pavement.
