OL,3,CTeenager locked up after officer left
OL,4,C'fearing for his life' during riots
OL,6,FBut, Judge Jeremy Richardson KC said
OL,7,Fhe had taken into account the
OL,8,Fdefendant's age and his apparent
OL,9,F"deplorable upbringing".
OL,11,FHe also said he had taken into account
OL,12,Fthe fact that a number of other
OL,13,Fdefendants involved in the rioting
OL,14,Fwould be coming before the court for
OL,15,Fmore serious offences.
OL,17,FBut, he added, it must be "made clear"
OL,18,Fthat all those participating in the
OL,19,Funrest would be "punished severely" by
OL,20,Fthe courts.
