OL,3,CTeenager locked up after officer left
OL,4,C'fearing for his life' during riots
OL,6,FSentencing, the judge told the
OL,7,Fdefendant: "You were a part of this
OL,8,Fmob of ignorant and violent
OL,9,Findividuals ... the scene was volatile
OL,10,Fand you were adding to the volatility.
OL,12,F"The officer (in the van) was scared
OL,13,Ffor his life and thought the vehicle
OL,14,Fwould be turned over, which was
OL,15,Fclearly your aim.
OL,17,F"You have brought shame on yourself
OL,18,Fand the town in which you live. You
OL,19,Fmust be punished for what you have
OL,20,Fdone."
